        <h2>Geography</h2>
        <p>New Grove City lies along the Silver River valley, surrounded by rolling hills and fertile farmland.</p>

        <h2>Climate</h2>
        <p>The city has a humid temperate climate, with warm summers and cool winters. Fog is common in autumn along the river.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Average summer: 27°C</li>
          <li>Average winter: 4°C</li>
